#
### Name: Borderlands 3 Tweaks and Fixes
### Version: 1
### Author: UnrealMe
### Categories: Bug Fixes, General QoL, UI Changes, Quests Tweaks, Loot Pool Tweaks.
### Description: This is a collection of mods containing bug fixes and quality of life improvements.
### This mod was created based on the Balands mod (Credits to Aaron0000), also includes many mods from all over the community.
### it is meant to be a similar experience to a Gearbox patch.
