### License URL: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/.
### CREDITS: Aaron0000, shadowevil, Apocalyptech, CZ47, Lonemastereno, EpicNNG, SSpyR, dex_manly, Elektrohund, ZetaDaemon, Novenic, Grimm
#


###################
### QoL Changes ###
###################

