SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_DemolitionWoman/FireInTheSkagDen/PassiveSkill_Gunner_FireInSkagDen.Default__PassiveSkill_Gunner_FireInSkagDen_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Whenever Moze or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] deals [skillbold]Splash Damage[/skillbold], they deal bonus [skillbold]Incendiary Damage[/skillbold].
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_DemolitionWoman/SteelHardpoints/Passive_Gunner_Deadlines.Default__Passive_Gunner_Deadlines_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Firing [actionskill]Iron Bear Weapons[/actionskill] [skillbold]drains less Fuel[/skillbold].<br><br>Killing an enemy while [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] is active increases [skillbold]Fuel[/skillbold]. This skill has diminishing returns.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_DemolitionWoman/Grizzled/PassiveSkill_Gunnerner_Grizzled.Default__PassiveSkill_Gunnerner_Grizzled_C:StatDataItems_UIStatData_OakPassiveAbilityAttribute,FormatText.string,0,,[skillbold]Action Skill Cooldown Time:[/skillbold] $VALUE$ seconds
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_DemolitionWoman/MeansOfDestruction/PassiveSkill_Gunner_MeansOfDestruction.Default__PassiveSkill_Gunner_MeansOfDestruction_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Whenever Moze or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] deals [skillbold]Splash Damage[/skillbold], there is a chance to add ammo to Moze's currently equipped weapon’s magazine, with a smaller chance to return a grenade.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_DemolitionWoman/NewDemoPassive2/Passive_Gunner_TorgueCrossPromo.Default__Passive_Gunner_TorgueCrossPromo_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,All [skillbold]Splash Damage[/skillbold] dealt by Moze or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] has a chance to [skillbold]double[/skillbold] in size. Additionally, Moze and [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] deal increased [skillbold]Splash Damage[/skillbold].
