SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/Augments/Augment_Core_5.Augment_Core_5,Description.string,0,,After Moze exits [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill] or [actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] ends, it will remain deployed in place for a short time.<br><br>While [actionskill]Auto Bear[/actionskill] remains active, it will target and attack nearby enemies until its duration ends, then it will charge at an enemy and self-destruct.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_DemolitionWoman/NewDemoPassive/Passive_Gunner_Vampyr.Default__Passive_Gunner_Vampyr_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Whenever Moze damages an enemy with a thrown grenade or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] deals area damage, for every enemy hit, she [skillbold]restores[/skillbold] a portion of their missing health. [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] receives half this bonus.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Passives/_Tree_UrsaCorps/FullCan/Passive_Gunner_FullCan.Default__Passive_Gunner_FullCan_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Entering [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill] or deploying [actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] causes Moze’s and her allies’ shields to immediately begin [skillbold]recharging[/skillbold] at an increased [skillbold]Shield Recharge Rate[/skillbold].
