SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_DLC/Ixora/Passives/DLCSkill_06/Passive_Gunner_DLCSkill_6.Default__Passive_Gunner_DLCSkill_6_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Moze and [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill] gain increased [skillbold]Status Effect Damage[/skillbold] and [skillbold]Status Effect Chance[/skillbold]. <br><br>[italic](Skill currently fully ineffective!)[/italic]
