# Make certain explosive Hard Points mention that they do not harm Moze or Iron Bear/Iron Cub.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/Augments/Augment_Mod_Missiles_3.Augment_Mod_Missiles_3,Description.string,0,,Instead of a volley of conventional rockets, the [actionskill]Vanquisher Rocket Pod[/actionskill] launches a single rocket with a nuclear warhead, dealing massive [skillbold]Radiation Damage[/skillbold]. This Hard Point cannot directly harm Moze or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill].
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/Augments/Augment_Mod_Missiles_3.Augment_Mod_Missiles_3,StatDataItems.StatDataItems[0].Object..bDisplayPlusSign,0,,true
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/Augments/Augment_Mod_Railgun_3.Augment_Mod_Railgun_3,Description.string,0,,[actionskill]Railgun[/actionskill] now fires a specialty round that deals reduced damage and explodes after a short delay.<br><br>[actionskill]Railgun[/actionskill] shots have reduced [skillbold]Fuel Drain[/skillbold] and the [skillbold]Magazine Size[/skillbold] is increased. The explosion cannot directly harm Moze or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill].
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/Augments/Augment_Mod_Fist_1.Augment_Mod_Fist_1,Description.string,0,,Whenever [actionskill]Bear Fist[/actionskill] hits an enemy, it deals random bonus [skillbold]Elemental Damage[/skillbold] to that enemy and all enemies nearby. The explosion cannot directly harm Moze or [actionskill]Iron Bear[/actionskill]/[actionskill]Iron Cub[/actionskill].

# Rakk Attack - Add a note saying that this Action Skill and its augments receive Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Beastmaster/_Shared/_Design/Character/ActionSkills/Skill1_RakkAttack/ActionSkill/ActionSkill_RakkAttack.Default__ActionSkill_RakkAttack_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,FL4K sends forward 2 [actionskill]Rakk[/actionskill] to dive-bomb enemies.<br><br>This skill has multiple charges.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] and its [actionskill]Augments[/actionskill] receive [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Trap Card - Change description to mention how it throws out a free trap.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Beastmaster/_DLC/Ixora/ActionSkill/Augments/Augment_Beastmaster_DLCSkill_Mod3.Augment_Beastmaster_DLCSkill_Mod3,Description.string,0,,If FL4K would go into [skillbold]Fight For Your Life[/skillbold] while their [actionskill]Trap[/actionskill] is readied, they [skillbold]automatically throw a free Trap[/skillbold] at the enemy that downed them.

# Anima - Update Description to mention it doesn't work with Cold Hearted.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Passives/ManifestTree/Anima/PassiveSkill_Siren_Anima.Default__PassiveSkill_Siren_Anima_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Amara's [skillbold]Status Effects[/skillbold] deal increased damage over time and have increased duration. Her [skillbold]Action Skill Status Effect[/skillbold] deals further increased damage. <br><br>[italic](Anima is rendered useless by [bold]Cold Hearted[/bold], Amara's Cryo Element.)[/italic]

# Sustainment - Make description more accurate.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Passives/ManifestTree/Sustainment/Passive_Siren_Sustainment.Default__Passive_Siren_Sustainment_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Amara gains [skillbold]Life Steal[/skillbold] whenever she deals [skillbold]Elemental Damage[/skillbold]. This does not include bonus elemental damage from skills, gear, or anointments.

# Forceful Expression - Update Description to be more accurate.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Passives/ManifestTree/Empowered/PassiveSkill_Siren_Empowered.Default__PassiveSkill_Siren_Empowered_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,Amara gains [skillbold]Bonus Elemental Damage[/skillbold] to all damage dealt [italic](except Melee and Vehicle Damage)[/italic], based on her [skillbold]Action Skill Element[/skillbold].

# Burn Both Ends - Update description to mention it boosts Elemental Damage and Kinetic Damage.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,2,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_DLC/Ixora/Passives/Table_Siren_DLCPassiveConstantValues.Table_Siren_DLCPassiveConstantValues,DLCSkill16_StackDuration,Base_17_28B25EC8493D1EB6C2138A962F659BCD,0,,10
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,2,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_DLC/Ixora/Passives/DLCSkill_16/Passive_Siren_DLCSkill_16.Default__Passive_Siren_DLCSkill_16_C,AbilityDescription.string,0,,After activating her [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill], Amara gains [skillbold]Increased Threat[/skillbold] for a short time, drawing the attention of all enemies in a huge radius.<br><br>Whenever Amara is dealt damage by an enemy, she gains increased [skillbold]Kinetic and Elemental Damage[/skillbold] for a short time. This effect stacks.

# Phaseflare - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receives Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_DLC/Ixora/Phasetrance/Augments/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC1_Phaseflare.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC1_Phaseflare,Description.string,0,,Amara summons an [actionskill]Orb of Elemental Energy[/actionskill] that deals constant [skillbold]elemental damage[/skillbold] to nearby enemies. Pressing {OakPC_Melee} near the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] causes it to [skillbold]fly forwards towards an enemy[/skillbold] and [skillbold]damage them[/skillbold]. Additionally, every time Amara uses a melee attack on the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill], it gains [skillbold]Increased Damage[/skillbold] based on the damage she dealt to it.<br><br>Pressing {OakPC_ActionSkill} causes the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] to return to Amara.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Tandava - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receives Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Phasetrance/Components/Attack/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Cast_100Fists.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Cast_100Fists,Description.string,0,,Amara sends forward an [actionskill]Astral Projection[/actionskill] of herself. When it hits a target, it [skillbold]explodes[/skillbold], damaging all nearby enemies.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Phaseslam - add a note saying that this Action Skill receives Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Phasetrance/Components/Attack/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Slam.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Slam,Description.string,0,,Amara leaps into the air and [actionskill]Slams[/actionskill] the ground, dealing damage to all nearby enemies and knocking them up.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Fracture - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receive Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Phasetrance/Components/Attack/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Slam_Fracture.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Slam_Fracture,Description.string,0,,Amara summons a [skillbold]line of fists[/skillbold] that erupt from the ground, dealing damage to enemies in front of Amara.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Downfall - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receive Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Phasetrance/Components/Attack/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Slam_Barrage.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_Slam_Barrage,Description.string,0,,Amara leaps into the air and shoots an [skillbold]Elemental Beam[/skillbold] below her briefly, followed by a [actionskill]Slam[/actionskill].<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Glow Up - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receive Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_DLC/Ixora/Phasetrance/Augments/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC2_GlowUp.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC2_GlowUp,Description.string,0,,Instead of dealing [skillbold]Splash Damage[/skillbold] to enemies, Amara's [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] grants nearby allies [skillbold]Health Regeneration[/skillbold]. Amara may also press {OakPC_Melee} while near the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] to send it to a downed ally, granting them a [skillbold]Second Wind[/skillbold].<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses despite what the description says.)[/italic]

# Shooting Star - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receive Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_DLC/Ixora/Phasetrance/Augments/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC7_SStar.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC7_SStar,Description.string,0,,Amara summons an [actionskill]Orb of Elemental Energy[/actionskill] that deals constant [skillbold]elemental damage[/skillbold] to nearby enemies. Pressing {OakPC_Melee} near the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] causes it to [skillbold]fly forwards towards an enemy[/skillbold] and [skillbold]damage them[/skillbold] which also increases the amount of [skillbold]Overall Damage[/skillbold] the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] deals to enemies. Additionally, the [actionskill]Elemental Orb[/actionskill] continually fires [skillbold]Elemental Projectiles[/skillbold] at the last enemy Amara damaged. Pressing {OakPC_ActionSkill} causes the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] to return to Amara.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

# Light Fantastic - Add a note saying that this Action Skill receive Splash bonuses.
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_DLC/Ixora/Phasetrance/Augments/Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC5_LFant.Augment_PhaseTrance_Attack_DLC5_LFant,Description.string,0,,Amara summons an [actionskill]Orb of Elemental Energy[/actionskill] that deals constant [skillbold]elemental damage[/skillbold] to nearby enemies. Whenever Amara damages an enemy, the [actionskill]Elemental Orb[/actionskill] automatically travels to that enemy. Whenever Amara kills an enemy, the [actionskill]Elemental Orb[/actionskill] gains [skillbold]Increased Damage[/skillbold]. Pressing {OakPC_ActionSkill} causes the [actionskill]Orb[/actionskill] to return to Amara.<br><br>[italic](This [actionskill]Action Skill[/actionskill] receives [skillbold]Splash[/skillbold] bonuses.)[/italic]

